    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simple rhythm game created by a Unity beginner! All you have to do is press the falling notes in time with the rhythm!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The initial 43 songs include &quot;Shining star&quot;, &quot;Cat life&quot;, &quot;SUMMER TRIANGLE&quot; and other free BGM often heard on Youtube, etc. The game has a large volume of songs! The fun of rhythm games is maintained, but the image of a hardcore sound game is given a cute atmosphere, making it easy for even those who have never played a sound game to play along with familiar tunes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scores are saved for each song, so those who are used to playing sound games can compete with each other for ranking. In addition, since the randomization function of the notes is implemented, the same song can be permanently enjoyed with hundreds or thousands of different patterns of music!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are three difficulty levels for each song: &quot;Easy,&quot; &quot;Normal,&quot; and &quot;Hard,&quot; so both beginners and experienced players can enjoy playing rhythm games at a level that suits their abilities. Whether you are a music game lover or have never played music games before, you should definitely try this game!</p>",
